column5: Well if you're getting really specific...  I went to the gym today too.  Then brought my puppy to the vet. On the way home she got carsick and barfed in my lap.  Spent 3 hours cleaning and organizing my man cave.  Cooked dinner for the clan and cleaned up.  Just checked on the dog a minute ago and found she had laid a huge poop right inside my shoe.  An eventful day all around.
Work wise, it was very eventfull as usuall I could be specific as to the details, but im sure the mods will be  As of right now, chatting and checking the threads and my emails.
